Class CompositionShape

java.lang.Object
org.example.my_project.Models.Shape
org.example.my_project.Models.CompositionShape
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class CompositionShape extends Shape implements Serializable
Represents a composition relationship between two class shapes. The shape is rendered as a line with a solid diamond at the starting class.

Composition indicates a strong ownership relationship where the lifecycle of the child class is tightly coupled with the parent class.
